 {\n                setState(() {\n                  _value = value;\n                });\n              },\n              selectionMode: CalendarSelectionMode.single,\n              // Provide a \"today\" reference for visual emphasis.\n              now: DateTime.now(),\n            ),\n          ],\n        ),\n      ),\n    );\n  }\n}\n",
);

Widget _buildCalendarExample2(BuildContext context) {
  return const CalendarExample2();
}

