tState(() {\n                  _value = value;\n                });\n              },\n              now: DateTime.now(),\n              // Disable all selection (view-only).\n              selectionMode: CalendarSelectionMode.none,\n            ),\n          ],\n        ),\n      ),\n    );\n  }\n}\n",
